team.description:
GDG(Google Developer Groups) is a global program across the world run by an individual group to inspire, help and grow a local community to adopt the Google technology and contribute to science.

DevFest Auburn is organized by GDG Cloud Auburn with support from Department of Computer Science and Software Engineering, Auburn University.
